From: Yang Shi <yang.shi@windriver.com>
Date: Mon, 9 Aug 2010 14:32:42 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 06/14] powerpc: mpc85xx: Add EERPOM dts node for P1022DS board

An AT24C02 EEPROM resides on i2c bus #2 0x57 which stores board
specific data, like mac address, etc.

Signed-off-by: Yang Shi <yang.shi@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p1022ds.dts |    4 ++++
 1 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p1022ds.dts b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p1022ds.dts
index a7c2c47..8cf3451 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p1022ds.dts
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/p1022ds.dts
@@ -151,6 +151,10 @@
 			interrupts = <43 2>;
 			interrupt-parent = <&mpic>;
 			dfsrr;
+			eeprom@57 {
+				compatible = "atmel,24c02";
+				reg = <0x57>;
+			};
 			rtc@68 {
 				compatible = "dallas,ds3232";
 				reg = <0x68>;
